DesktopSize 1x1

# Disable changing desktop when mouse is near edge
EdgeScroll 0 0

# Focus: Focus changes only on click
Style * FPClickToFocus, MouseFocusClickRaises, !FPEnterToFocus, !FPLeaveToUnfocus

###  Key binding contexts
# A = All
# R = Root
# W = Window

###  Modifiers
# A = Any
# C = Control
# S = Shift
# M = Meta
# N = None
# 4 = Alt?

### Window switching / resizing
# Alt + h,j,k,l :  Move focus in direction
Key H A M Direction West  Focus
Key K A M Direction South Focus
Key J A M Direction North Focus
Key L A M Direction East  Focus

Key H A SM MoveToWindowWest
Key J A SM MoveToWindowSouth
Key K A SM MoveToWindowNorth
Key L A SM MoveToWindowEast

AddToFunc SaveWindowFrameCoords
+ I SetEnv fvwm_window_n $[w.y]
+ I SetEnv fvwm_window_s $[w.y] + $[w.height]
+ I SetEnv fvwm_window_e $[w.x] + $[w.width]
+ I SetEnv fvwm_window_w $[w.x]

AddToFunc UnsetWindowFrameCoords
+ I UnsetEnv fvwm_window_n
+ I UnsetEnv fvwm_window_s
+ I UnsetEnv fvwm_window_e
+ I UnsetEnv fvwm_window_w

AddToFunc MoveToWindowEast
+ I ScanForWindow East North SaveWindowFrameCoords
+ I Move $[fvwm_window_w]-$[w.width]p keep
+ I UnsetWindowFrameCoords

AddToFunc MoveToWindowWest
+ I ScanForWindow West North SaveWindowFrameCoords
+ I Move $[fvwm_window_e]p keep
+ I UnsetWindowFrameCoords

AddToFunc MoveToWindowSouth
+ I ScanForWindow South West SaveWindowFrameCoords
+ I Move  keep $[fvwm_window_n]-$[w.height]p
+ I UnsetWindowFrameCoords

AddToFunc MoveToWindowNorth
+ I ScanForWindow North West SaveWindowFrameCoords
+ I Move keep $[fvwm_window_s]p
+ I UnsetWindowFrameCoords


Key Space W M Maximize 0 grow

### Theme
Colorset 3 fg #101060, bg #e6e7d7
Colorset 4 fg Black, bg #a6a797
Colorset 5 fg White, bg Black

DestroyDecor MyDecor
AddToDecor   MyDecor
+ TitleStyle LeftJustified Height 18
+ TitleStyle -- Flat
+ BorderStyle Simple -- NoInset Flat
+ ButtonStyle All -- UseTitleStyle

Style "*" UseDecor MyDecor, NoHandles, BorderWidth 2, TitleAtBottom

DestroyFunc drag-n-move 
AddToFunc drag-n-move M move 
DestroyFunc drag-n-resize 
AddToFunc drag-n-resize M resize 
Mouse 1 W M drag-n-move 
Mouse 3 W M drag-n-resize 
